 </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104339Q2yvZcfDBhxG5adn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104339ac8GzBOFIstS0PfT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271043399fNj7dxErkbVSh83.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104340vp6z5dRqweofPm4r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271043393Pv0WLm7AdCteugj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104340dGsmW2phUJYl8nXu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104340whdtQgVWMyGcNI8B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104341yhfaYrqKVJmEw0Ti.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104342FgQ52NkBfr03OvPp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104340vDbWImJZCilNM4hR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104342ZaDCYFK8piwg4nl9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104343fwFiWuoBlNRGnh5X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104343pGyh0UzxWcQN7PYq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271043439sy5t7afh8BT3G14.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104343yznmqPtr5pxYWOE6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104344KMJCL6vIRnQGN840.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104341HLRFeC7V2KBJyftM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>性冷淡鼻祖&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/06/26/acne-studios-ss18-mens-pfw/#slide-25\" rel=\"nofollow\">Acne Studios 也带来了 2018 春夏男装系列</a>。不过，这一次它并没有“走秀”，而是别出心裁地让男模特全部坐下来，由观众自行走动、拍照。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104434avecqBg9KTUYERm6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104434ltcRCAqQ6dLDkEUu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104434Re8wLIvGHBay49f6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104434MUWAvlxzgr6u1eH7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104434ItEuMcv7CQsqnUX4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104435aS0U5d7o4X6EcyBH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104435Cbz0spu8OVB6AvJa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104436evs96dcoSxH2gU7O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104