style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104440pVJ05y4ktnOeCRFK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627104509S7soUf3d6XE8htMB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/article/paris-fashion-week-birkenstock\" rel=\"nofollow\">Birkenstock 去了巴黎时装周做宣传展示，这是品牌成立 242 年来的“首秀”</a>。时装周现场，Birkenstock 在 Tuileries 花园搭了一个舞台，它有着松木制成的 T 台和环绕周围的植物，40 个模特展示了 115 双不同款式的勃肯鞋。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105128P6B5SUxJVktnuYec.png\" data-ratio=\"1.003745\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105054tkTvmdcF6ipfK5jB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271050540njdPaM6KBN7if3s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017062710505441wC7IfpkW9Ml3Ui.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105055lqXxTe8ArJLhC43i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105055m1JcbWt8wsQTfiMY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105055j5hNknTK8avr34YD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706271050550oabwyBWFARvQ8ck.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105056vBPiylITsahbLCNq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105056TOD2SKqQY4G5vxLd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105056lpA4mLGB9IbaiOof.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105056yPwv4rf07UC8jt5Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105057oak1qvTrIwhM0tZV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105057cQtMJg9D6umalrvb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105058wGSMlcjrgDpqfkCZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170627105057xE9iTw8clJ24K0yM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/kith-x-coca-cola-x-converse-chuck-taylor-1970s-first-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}